erver; no external service is required. Avoid optional OAuth2-specific coverage unless adding its optional Vert.x auth dependency deliberately.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Without the Netty/JDK 25 system properties, native-image run can fail even when the generated WebClient tests are otherwise valid.\",\n    \"Testing optional paths such as `OAuth2WebClient` may require optional dependencies not needed for normal WebClient coverage.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0ff5c533d31d9170016a3ee01af7f88197a0d51b0b0cbe2772\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1932, "output": 756, "cacheRead": 23552, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 26240, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782505487369, "responseId": "resp_0ff5c533d31d9170016a3ee010a9a48197a8fdfe16b5f69bf9"}, "toolResults": []}
